<html><head><title>New Hot Zone Information</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>New Hot Zone Information</h3><p>Developer Nodyin wrote in response to a question about when the new hot zones will be rolled out:<br><br>"...We'll probably have one more patch in the next week or so to fix some lingering TSS issues but the new Hot Zones won't be ready until the first normal patch about a month or so after the launch of TSS.<br><br>I can give you this teaser though - Merloc had some really cool ideas for itemization for the next set of zones that I'm pretty excited about and I think the zones selected will be a lot of fun."<br> </div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Friday, 29 September, 2006<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=21636">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=21636</a><br>Printed On: Tue Oct 17 23:47:37 PDT 2006<br>©2005 IGN Entertainment</font></span>